                            <comment id="14567348" author="rcatherinot" created="Mon, 1 Jun 2015 14:24:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Isolate HashMap accesses by using ThreadLocal + added javadoc to state the class is thread-safe. No unit tests because it&apos;s not possible to reproduce it on demand.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14567559" author="rcatherinot" created="Mon, 1 Jun 2015 16:48:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;cannot be easily reproduced, need a real multi-core machine within a JVM with lots of threads using parsing several queries at the same time to have a chance to encounter the bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15257051" author="rohini" created="Mon, 25 Apr 2016 21:04:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. Verified that TestMRCompiler and TestTezCompiler are good. Committed to trunk. Thanks for the contribution Remi.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
